    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly driver with plenty of usable life left and good bones for someone who knows their way around a wrench. Engine fires up, runs, and the car has the kind of straightforward mechanical layout that makes it a great commuter, backup vehicle, or light project. Cosmetically it shows age and wear, but underneath that is a practical car with real value for the money. If you want inexpensive transportation with potential and don\u2019t mind a little cleanup and sorting, this one is worth a look.",
